<i>by one simple spark.</i>

27
00:01:28,600 --> 00:01:31,799
<i>He was tamping down
an explosive charge with an iron rod</i>

28
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,260
<i>when the gunpowder ignited early</i>

29
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,417
<i>and a three-foot iron rod</i>

30
00:01:36,542 --> 00:01:39,139
<i>was blown clear
through Phineas' skull.</i>

31
00:01:39,451 --> 00:01:41,977
<i>Miraculously, Phineas survived.</i>

32
00:01:45,566 --> 00:01:48,616
<i>His body, it seemed,
had made a complete recovery.</i>

33
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:51,473
<i>His spirit, on the other hand...</i>

34
00:01:56,651 --> 00:01:58,432
<i>Those who knew Phineas' best</i>

35
00:01:58,557 --> 00:02:01,428
<i>said he was a changed man
after his accident.</i>

36
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:03,939
<i>Once even-keeled and hardworking,</i>

37
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:07,710
<i>he was now fitful, irreverent
and grossly profane.</i>

38
00:02:08,267 --> 00:02:10,184
<i>But would it surprise you to learn</i>

39
00:02:10,309 --> 00:02:13,200
