41
00:02:16,298 --> 00:02:17,962
<i>as "Cyrus Ames"?</i>

42
00:02:18,570 --> 00:02:21,218
<i>Who, you ask, was Cyrus Ames?</i>

43
00:02:21,934 --> 00:02:25,740
<i>Cyrus Ames was a notorious
gunfighter and card cheat.</i>

44
00:02:26,154 --> 00:02:28,651
<i>For a time, he was employed
by the railroads</i>

45
00:02:28,776 --> 00:02:32,305
<i>to shoot any Indians who attempted
to interfere with the construction.</i>

46
00:02:32,909 --> 00:02:35,059
<i>On the day of Phineas' accident,</i>

47
00:02:35,309 --> 00:02:37,926
