51
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:49,175
<i>That the soul of a dying gunfighter</i>

52
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:53,146
<i>somehow slipped into the body
of an injured railroad worker.</i>

53
00:02:53,926 --> 00:02:56,611
<i>Coincidence?
We may never know.</i>

54
00:02:57,448 --> 00:02:59,007
<i>Unlikely? Yes.</i>

55
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:02,051
<i>Impossible?
You be the judge.</i>

56
00:03:02,729 --> 00:03:05,412
<i>A man by the name of
Robert l. Ripley, after all,</i>

57
